    <title>arthas用法</title>
    <link href="/2024/02/24/arthas%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95/"/>
    <url>/2024/02/24/arthas%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="arthas"><a href="#arthas" class="headerlink" title="arthas"></a>arthas</h4><ol><li><code>trace</code>：查询最耗时应用</li></ol><p>​trace *.CraftParaAlarmRateServiceImpl getCraftParaAlarmRate</p><ol start="2"><li><code>jad</code>：反编译耗时代码</li></ol><p>​jad *.CraftParaAlarmRateServiceImpl getCraftParaAlarmRate</p><ol start="3"><li><p><code>watch</code>：捕获耗时应用入参、返回值</p></li><li><p><code>redefine</code>：用于热修复问题或在不停止应用程序的情况下修改类的行为（）</p></li></ol><p>​redefine -c <className> -b &#x2F;path&#x2F;to&#x2F;new&#x2F;classfile</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
